            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Silvanus Augustus. In honour of Marcus Trosius Daphnis, sexvir, and Marcus Trosius Cissus, freedman. Marcus Trosius Modestus, gave (this) gift.</p>
